instructions: put the dinner plate on the bottom side of the table cloth
put the fork on the left side of the dinner point with it's prongs facing up
put the salad fork to the left of the dinner fork with it's prongs facing up
put the dinner knife on the right side of the dinner plate with it's blade facing the dinner plate
put the salad knife to the right of the dinner knife with its blade facing towards the salad knife
put the soup spoon to the right of the salad knife with its bowl facing up
put the glass in front of the dinner knife's blade, in between the dinner plate and the dinner knife
put the wine glass to the right of the water glass, in front of the soup spoon
put the second wine glass to the right of the first wine glass
put the coffee cup to the right of the soup spoon, behind the second wine glass
put the bread plate in front of the dinner and salad forks
put the butter knife diagonally on the top right part of the bread plate facing away from the dinner
put the dessert fork in front of the dinner plate, with its prongs facing the water glass
put the dessert spoon in front of the dessert fork with its bowl upward facing the bread plate
Put the napkin vertically in the center of the dinner plate
